text: Chas V. Vincent (born July 24, 1977) is a Republican State Senator in the Montana Legislature from District 1 representing Libby, Montana. He is a graduate of the University of Montana. == See also == * Montana House of Representatives District 2 ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Loggers from Montana Category:Montana Republicans Category:Montana state senators Category:University of Montana alumni Category:People from Kalispell, Montana Category:People from Libby, Montana Category:21st-century American politicians
